description: Retrieves details of the specified Amazon Web Services-managed view.

parameters.name: ManagedViewArn
parameters.description: The Amazon resource name (ARN) of the managed view.

nested_items.name: ManagedView
nested_items.description: Details about the specified managed view.

nested_items.name: FilterString
nested_items.description: The string that contains the search keywords, prefixes, and operators to control the results that can be returned by a  Search operation. For more details, see Search query syntax.

nested_items.name: IncludedProperties
nested_items.description: A structure that contains additional information about the managed view.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the property that is included in this view.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time when this managed view was last modified.

nested_items.name: ManagedViewArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon resource name (ARN) of the managed view.

nested_items.name: ManagedViewName
nested_items.description: The name of the managed view.

nested_items.name: Owner
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account that owns this managed view.

nested_items.name: ResourcePolicy
nested_items.description: The resource policy that defines access to the managed view. To learn more about this policy, review Managed views.

nested_items.name: Scope
nested_items.description: An Amazon resource name (ARN) of an Amazon Web Services account or organization that specifies whether this managed view includes resources from only the specified Amazon Web Services account or all accounts in the specified organization.

nested_items.name: TrustedService
nested_items.description: The service principal of the Amazon Web Services service that created and manages the managed view.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The version of the managed view.
